      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, I'm definitely worried about those hidden traps. It feels like certain corporations use this kind of language to sneak in unfair terms that aren't obvious at first glance. Can you give me an example of how a \"sneaky\" clause like this might actually play out in a real dispute? Like, how does the \"hidden\" part work in practice?",
